{"tid":755874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知有無人都鍾意摸耳仔","createTime":"2018-07-25T14:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T03:54:34.000Z","uid":167369,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"02211f4d1f8bea4c8d1d130af06687ff8984239b","tid":755874,"uid":167369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:19:33.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好鍾意摸隻耳仔<br />\n無論自己定其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都好鍾意個種涼涼地嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n摸自己個陣 鍾意一野捲埋佢塞入個耳窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚唔摸都訓唔著<br />\n仲會上癮到行行下街都摸<br />\n啲人以為我起到整耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人都係咁架呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相認下"},{"pid":"1bfb31993af487ed00450a8ee18cf7966719088f","tid":755874,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:21:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e9298d0cc73cfff1684e30f5968ebee2fe3d040","tid":755874,"uid":102485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"我本身耳珠比較厚肉<br />\n中學有個幾fd嘅女同學好中意玩<br />\n個感覺好痕 但又爽爽地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bdfd6cdcf023c5f79a7610a1cb57ab5fd38502","tid":755874,"uid":91093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"我都係由細摸到大"},{"pid":"c10cf10ea5a5cf8838873272b37f1152f280f81f","tid":755874,"uid":164980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63cb255143ef2780ca378a2c572ef6df4d3c9746","tid":755874,"uid":8304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"病徵一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇得醫了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/to